'''Betsy Mitchell''' has been the editor-in-chief of [[Del Rey]] Books since [[2002]]. Previously, she was the Associate Publisher of [[Bantam Spectra]] when they held the license to publish ''Star Wars'' novels in the 1990s. She edited many of the books from this period, including [[Timothy Zahn]]'s ''[[Heir to the Empire]]''.

